Merge branch 'master' of github.com:py-yyc/python-dojo-4-tkinter
Added presentation slides

Code for python dojo 4
Cleaned out the master branch to make space for dojo contents; added a .gitignore for python projects; modified the readme to explain the reason for this repository
Merge branch 'master' of github.com:bmcmurray/hekyll
Add page break divs for printing slides.
Add a link to the history of Hekyll.
Add syntax highlighting support.
Update readme to add theme support as a goal.
Add the ability to set an id attribute to the slide for fine-tuned control of the URL hash, or to ease styling your slide.
Move partials into the hekyll theme.
Move CSS into a new theme's folder in preparation for a few simple alternate designs.

Merge pull request #15 from bmcmurray/Simple_Slideshow

Simple Slideshow
Simple Slideshow. Add a new simple-slideshow configuration option to ignore slide position and just cross-fade between slides. Neato!

Merge pull request #13 from smerrill/print-styles

Print CSS!
Add print styles for page breaks.
Merge branch 'master' of github.com:bmcmurray/hekyll
Add a basic print page that doesn't include the impress.js script.

Merge pull request #10 from smerrill/list-style-fixes

Add default styles.
Add default list, header styles.
Handle empty title better, print title of slide in H1.
Update README with more instructions. Add classes to frontmatter for more flexibility.

Merge pull request #9 from bmcmurray/Overview

Overview Slide
Update overview to take arbitrary data attributes like slides.
Remove default posts from master so it's easier to merge into other presentation projects.
Update source documentation slide since we don't need gh-pages-source branch any longer.
Use Compass CSS3 mixins instead of manual CSS3 declarations.
Overview Slide: A new configuration option to add an overview slide at the end, prezi style.
